-      "description": "Create `backend/src/main/java/com/weeklycommit/ai/rag/SemanticQueryService.java`:\n- Spring `@Service`.\n- Constructor injects `PineconeClient`, `EmbeddingService`, `AiProviderRegistry`, `AiSuggestionService`, `ObjectMapper`.\n- Public method `RagQueryResult query(String question, UUID teamId, UUID userId)`:\n  1. Check PineconeClient.isAvailable() and EmbeddingService.isAvailable(); if either is false, return unavailable result.\n  2. Intent classification: call AiProviderRegistry.generateSuggestion() with an AiContext of type \"RAG_INTENT\" containing the question. Parse the LLM response to extract `{ intent, userFilter, timeRange, entityTypes, keywords }`. If parsing fails, use defaults (no filters, all entity types).\n  3. Embed the question via EmbeddingService.embed(question).\n  4. Build Pinecone metadata filter from intent (e.g., filter by teamId, entityTypes, date range).\n  5. Query Pinecone: `pineconeClient.query(namespace, vector, topK=5, filter)`.\n  6. Pack retrieved chunks + original question into a new AiContext (type \"RAG_QUERY\") and call AiProviderRegistry.generateSuggestion().\n  7. Parse LLM response into structured answer: `{ answer, sources: [{entityType, entityId, weekStartDate, snippet}], confidence }`.\n  8. Store via AiSuggestionService.storeSuggestion() with type \"RAG_QUERY\".\n  9. Return RagQueryResult.\n- Add \"RAG_INTENT\" and \"RAG_QUERY\" type constants to AiContext.\n- Inner record `RagQueryResult(boolean available, String answer, List<RagSource> sources, double confidence, UUID suggestionId)`.\n- Inner record `RagSource(String entityType, String entityId, String weekStartDate, String snippet)`.\n\nCreate prompt templates:\n- `backend/src/main/resources/prompts/rag-intent.txt` тАФ System prompt for intent classification.\n- `backend/src/main/resources/prompts/rag-query.txt` тАФ System prompt for RAG answer generation.\n\nUpdate `StubAiProvider.java` to handle the new \"RAG_INTENT\" and \"RAG_QUERY\" suggestion types with canned responses.\n\nCreate `backend/src/test/java/com/weeklycommit/ai/rag/SemanticQueryServiceTest.java`:\n- Unit test with mocked PineconeClient, EmbeddingService, AiProviderRegistry, AiSuggestionService.\n- Test successful query pipeline (mock each step to return valid data).\n- Test Pinecone unavailable returns unavailable result.\n- Test embedding failure returns unavailable.\n- Test LLM failure at intent step still proceeds with defaults.\n- Test result is stored via AiSuggestionService.",
